   =20
 =20
There was a viral TikTok=C2=A0about =E2=80=9Clooking for a man in finance, =
trust fund, six-five, blue eyes,=E2=80=9D so now, if you go to Phebe=E2=80=
=99s or the PJ Clarke=E2=80=99s by Brookfield Place, there is some chance t=
hat you will encounter a journalist doing a story about men in finance. Her=
e=E2=80=99s one from Joanna Rothkopf at the Cut:What of the humble finance =
bro who, for the record, didn=E2=80=99t ask for any of this? All he ever wa=
nted was to work through the best years of his life juiced up on a steady c=
ocktail of Adderall and whey protein until he had earned enough money to mi=
streat hotel staff. No one was thinking about how all this commotion affect=
ed him: Was he dating more? Less? Did he like being the center of attention=
?So she goes to the Spaniard, =E2=80=9Cdescribed to me as an =E2=80=98analy=
st bar=E2=80=99 in the West Village,=E2=80=9D and at first meets =E2=80=9Cm=
en who can=E2=80=99t possibly be bankers,=E2=80=9D because =E2=80=9Ctheir w=
ardrobe and grooming suggest they work in a creative-adjacent industry like=
 advertising or military contracting.=E2=80=9D Eventually she meets some mo=
re-or-less finance-y people:The first thing to know, the guys say, is that =
=E2=80=9Cfinance=E2=80=9D isn=E2=80=99t even what most people think it is a=
nymore. =E2=80=9CEveryone thinks, Oh, finance, but that=E2=80=99s just some=
thing they learn is prestigious in school,=E2=80=9D Dennis says. Because of=
 the earnings cap at a level like, say, managing director, he continues, =
=E2=80=9CYou could make way more by owning five bodegas.=E2=80=9D They all =
agree that owning five bodegas is a great way of making money, though it is=
 also a different sort of job.As for the meme, of course they know about it=
. =E2=80=9CI=E2=80=99m a manager; I gotta keep up with what the people I=E2=
=80=99m managing are talking about,=E2=80=9D Dennis says before showing me =
a tweet from @litcapital that reads, =E2=80=9CWhen you crushed 10 espresso =
martinis at The Spaniard last night and hungover staring at the screen all =
morning.=E2=80=9DMaybe a little weird for the manager to be at an analyst b=
ar but whatever.
